{
  "stem": "7093.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we formed a sabotage group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That is to say, I exaggerate when I say 'we formed.' But I have been asked to be a part, take-- take part in a sabotage group.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I only knew the one before me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't know who else was in the chain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I must say even that I forgot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know got me into there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But obviously they thought I was a reliable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And what happened, there were quite a few chemists amongst us, and they managed to get in to the so-called 'filling rooms,' where they prepared the mixture for the grenades and filled the-- the hulls with the mixture.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, of course, because they were chemists and knew how to change the quantities so that these mixtures shouldn't work and shouldn't be-- shouldn't explode.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They increased the production by threefold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now, before us there were German workers working in the factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They increased the production to threefold what the German workers did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Everybody complained.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "All the other women complained.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We worked together with Germans, and they complained because they never had to work so hard because it didn't-- the production never moved so hard.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But they increased the production threefold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the-- the foreman-- foreman, the German foreman, saw that the stupid Jewish women are so frightened that they work so hard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So the control became very superficial.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And because-- and-- and that's what we aimed at.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because through that, in the filling room, they could do with the mixture whatever they wanted, and they could change the mixture so that it couldn't explode.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
